# StatusBadge 状态徽标

> 用于状态指示与系统反馈的轻量徽标。  
> **状态**：Beta


## Demo
### Status Signals

成功/警告/错误/信息。

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="StatusBadgeSignalsDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxStatusBadge text="成功" status="success" />
    <TxStatusBadge text="警告" status="warning" />
    <TxStatusBadge text="错误" status="danger" />
    <TxStatusBadge text="信息" status="info" />
  </template>
---
::

## API（简版）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: text
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
    description: '显示文字'
  - name: status
    type: "'success' | 'warning' | 'danger' | 'info' | 'muted'"
    default: 'info'
    description: '状态类型'
  - name: statusKey
    type: "'granted' | 'denied' | 'notDetermined' | 'unsupported' | string"
    default: "''"
    description: '映射到色调的权限/状态键'
  - name: icon
    type: 'string'
    default: "''"
    description: '自定义图标 class'
  - name: size
    type: "'sm' | 'md'"
    default: 'md'
    description: '尺寸'
  - name: os
    type: "'macos' | 'windows' | 'linux'"
    default: '-'
    description: '可选平台图标'
  - name: osOnly
    type: 'boolean'
    default: 'false'
    description: '仅渲染平台图标'
---
::

## 契约说明

显式 `status` 优先于 `statusKey`。`statusKey` 会把 `granted/denied/notDetermined/unsupported` 映射到 success/danger/warning/muted，未知 key 回退到 info。平台图标会渲染在状态图标前；`osOnly` 会隐藏状态图标。点击徽标会触发 `click` 事件。

